  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Romantik Hotel Schweizerhof is offered on a half board basis with breakfast and dinner taken in the hotels restaurant.</p>
<p>Breakfast consists of a continental buffet with hot &amp; cold options.</p>
<p>Dinner includes a 4 course evening meal including salad, starter, a choice of main course and dessert or cheese. </p>
<p>A Christmas &amp; New Year gala dinner with live music is included.</p>
<p>Early meal times available for children from 6pm. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
  <deactivateThisPage>0</deactivateThisPage>
  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Romantik Hotel Schweizerhof has an enviable location near the train station and the complimentary hotel shuttle to and from the First ski lifts and free ski bus just outside ensures easy access to the ski areas. The hotel prides itself on high standards of service and cuisine, welcoming guests from the moment they step in and ensuring you have a comfortable and memorable stay.</p>
<h2>Comfortable mountain hotel</h2>
<p>Attractively furnished throughout, the hotel has a traditional chalet-style exterior and radiates charm in its beautiful mountain surroundings. Head inside for modern comforts and enjoy the spacious public areas. The lobby lounge area has an open fireplace where you can enjoy the complimentary English afternoon tea, cake and sandwiches on offer, when you return from the mountains. </p>
<h2>Schweizerhof spa</h2>
<p>The spa facilities at the Romantik Schweizerhof are fantastic and offer a range of relaxation therapies. The general spa area includes access to an indoor pool, steam bath, Finnish sauna, glacier grotto and tropical rain shower. There are also opportunities for a massage or beauty treatments for an extra charge.</p>
<h2>Food and drink</h2>
<p>Romantik Hotel Schweizerhof offers fine and hearty homemade foods to get you through your day. Breakfast includes <span>daily homemade patisseries and a range of hot and cold foods. After you're back from your time on the slopes, dinner provides a 4 course evening menu with choice of main course. </span></p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
