  <locationDescription><![CDATA[<p>Romantik Hotel Schweizerhof is set in a quiet position in its own grounds, just a three minutes’ walk (350 metres) from the village centre and mountain railway station for access to the Kleine Scheidegg ski area.</p>
<p>The hotel offers a free shuttle bus to the ‘First’ lifts in the mornings between 8-11am and afternoons between 3-6pm. The free resort bus also stops just outside.</p>]]></locationDescription>
